(51,7%)
</p>
<p> 
</p><p> 
209. The statistics on the actual application of preventive measures further manifest 
positive developments in this respect. In the first nine months of 2007 non-custodial 
preventive measures have been applied in more than 55 per cent of cases. 
 
</p>
